 u(x,t) = \phi(x,t) + v(x,t)
u
\phi_x(0,t)=0 \text{ and }\phi(L,t)=\sin^2\frac{t}{2}.
\phi(x,t)=\sin^2\frac{t}{2},
u(x,t)=\sin^2\frac{t}{2}+v(x,t).
